text: Shanyn MacEachern (born 17 February 1980) is a Canadian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brampton
